data.description: Discover the charm of this adorable brick ranch featuring 3 bed, 3 bath, 1-car garage, & enough space for an RV. The updated kitchen boasts SS appliances, a double oven, & elegant hardwood & tile floors. Adjacent to the dining area is a delightful hot tub room leading to a private patio- perfect for entertaining! Basement includes an office, spacious great room, bathroom, laundry room, ample storage, & additional room. Don't miss the opportunity to make this home yours at an exceptional price!
